{"tid":1343570,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"721港共政府與元朗黑幫合作行動之對策 集思廣益","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T19:05:33.000Z","uid":39001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe670413fa5cf6eb5e5796c11c75a70590c9acec","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:00:26.000Z","msg":"當你是港共，已經冇能力以正當途徑消滅反對聲音，出低莊手段是合乎中共常理的。<br />\n而使用黑勢力能為港共政府帶來什麼影響？<br />\n以下為本人發夢斷尻估得出的幾個可能：<br />\n1. 讓我們需同時對付黑勢力黑狗。從而讓我們<span style=\"color: gold;\">失焦</span>，忘記我們最終最大的敵人。<br />\n2. 黑狗日後可能大舉捉拿黑勢力人士，<span style=\"color: gold;\">為黑狗洗白</span>，從而令市民感到「黑狗也未太黑」的假象。<br />\n3. 將示威者與黑勢力混為一談，黑狗高調捉人，一方面<span style=\"color: gold;\">造出白色恐怖</span>令義不再有所行動，另一方面<span style=\"color: gold;\">加劇社會矛盾</span>。<br />\n<br />\n小弟自細冇好好讀書，1999。希望大家可以一齊冷靜分析港共每一步嘅動機同目標，再計劃下一步行動。"},{"pid":"695899980fc9aa656c39756fd5a78c01efdb1895","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:01:05.000Z","msg":"討論下"},{"pid":"ca5b37036092e5759b1bf5f6e5be7828cc48ce65","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:01:17.000Z","msg":"點做好？"},{"pid":"117472cde11eaafbd2ca6c6cf24330e18900efa0","tid":1343570,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"正苦出左新聞犒，咪中左第3點囉"},{"pid":"182cb36aa44e30a15cfbeff2d0201ec79e68ddd0","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:01:42.000Z","msg":"研究下燒祠堂可行性"},{"pid":"15b39e8cc469b4a5bc8875067293b20458eaa4ae","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117472cde11eaafbd2ca6c6cf24330e18900efa0","tid":1343570,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"正苦出左新聞犒，咪中左第3點囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:02:09.000Z","msg":"未睇添，我去睇睇"},{"pid":"96fe1c27d2d014e243cff2184da353da637f79fd","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"ad530a7104ac24c0a1a2817c9fc976bc906826b9","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:03:31.000Z","msg":"唔想咁多自己人中晒港共嘅招數"},{"pid":"a1a6bc4c40cc84c821c6a8dd9f54f012f9b4dbd4","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:03:41.000Z","msg":"幫幫手"},{"pid":"255f62a24c1928d1474690abde58997bb7ffe402","tid":1343570,"uid":158504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca5b37036092e5759b1bf5f6e5be7828cc48ce65","tid":1343570,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:01:17.000Z","msg":"點做好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:05:33.000Z","msg":"我哋今日第一次出擊中聯辦噴鳩佢<br />\n嚇到中共驚到即刻出黑社會轉移視線，證明咗我哋方向正確<br />\n繼續目前行動，但矛頭直至中聯辦，將反共訊息推上國際"}]}